    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, but it's a bit high-level. could you dig deeper into the specific philosophical and practical arguments? for example, how would someone argue the link between national sovereignty and economic stability, or the moral argument regarding a state's primary duty to its own citizens? i really need those nuanced points so they don't get caught off guard by a well-constructed conservative case.",
